data/scratch/

# Note on data/inputs/:
# We intentionally commit the small static-directory inputs (CSVs ~5MB
# total, Fireflies meeting JSONs ~18MB) so Render free tier — which has
# no persistent disk — can rebuild crm.db on every cold start via the
# bootstrap script. Anything new + sensitive should be added to
# data/scratch/ instead.
